# CODEOWNERS file for macro-ai repository

# This file defines code ownership for automated review assignment and workflow access control

#

# Syntax: Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners

# Patterns are ordered from most specific to least specific

# The last matching pattern takes precedence

#

# For more information: <https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners>

